%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Student-loan%20borrowers%20struggling%20with%20repayment%20need%20more%20help%20than%20what%20the%20Education%20Department%20has%20offered%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they%20might%20not%20get%20it%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225346%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22President%20Joe%20Biden%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d51a9348a88f001969135e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223695%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EU.S.%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%3Cp%3EKevin%20Dietsch%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EStudent-loan%20companies%20have%20made%20a%20range%20of%20errors%20with%20borrowers'%20accounts%20over%20the%20past%20month.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Education%20Department%20is%20strengthening%20oversight%20by%20withholding%20pay%20from%20one%20servicer%2C%20MOHELA.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20it%20might%20not%20fully%20address%20the%20issues%20borrowers%20have%20when%20funding%20is%20already%20tight.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden's%20Education%20Department%20made%20one%20thing%20very%20clear%20this%20past%20week%3A%20Student-loan%20companies%20cannot%20get%20away%20with%20bad%20behavior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20might%20not%20fully%20solve%20the%20issues%20plaguing%20borrowers%20as%20they%20transition%20back%20into%20repayment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20Education%20Department%20announced%20it%20would%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-company-mohela-late-statements-borrowers-biden-withholding-pay-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewithholding%20over%20%247%20million%20in%20October%20pay%20from%20student-loan%20company%20MOHELA%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20company%20failed%20to%20deliver%20on-time%20billing%20statements%20to%202.5%20million%20borrowers%2C%20causing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmohela-student-loan-borrowers-missed-payments-forbearance-debt-education-department-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E800%2C000%20of%20them%20to%20fall%20into%20delinquency%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20made%20clear%20this%20was%20an%20oversight%20action%20to%20prevent%20servicers%20from%20making%20mistakes%20in%20the%20future%2C%20with%20a%20spokesperson%20telling%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20MOHELA's%20%26quot%3Bfailure%20to%20meet%20their%20basic%20obligation%20to%20borrowers%20and%20the%20Department%20will%20not%20be%20tolerated%20without%20consequence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20continue%20to%20fight%20for%20additional%20funding%20to%20support%20servicers%20and%20ensure%20better%20experience%20for%20borrowers%2C%20borrowers%20should%20be%20able%20to%20count%20on%20receiving%20timely%20and%20accurate%20information%20from%20their%20servicers%2C%20which%20is%20what%20this%20action%20aims%20to%20accomplish%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%20MOHELA%20has%20not%20publicly%20commented%20on%20the%20error.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20funding%2C%20or%20lack%20thereof%2C%20has%20been%20central%20to%20the%20conversation%20surrounding%20repayment%20errors%20and%20delays%20borrowers%20have%20been%20experiencing.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-company-mohela-extensive-servicing-delays-repayment-borrowers-warren-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMOHELA%20previously%20blamed%20the%20lack%20of%20additional%20funding%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Congress%20for%20Federal%20Student%20Aid%20to%20facilitate%20repayment%20operations%2C%20telling%20lawmakers%20in%20an%20August%20letter%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20immediacy%20of%20return-to-repayment%20amid%20ever-increasing%20changes%20to%20the%20contract%20administration%20requirements%20and%20expanded%20training%20needs%2C%20combined%20with%20the%20lack%20of%20sufficient%20funding%20from%20FSA%2C%20means%20extensive%20servicing%20delays%20are%20a%20likely%20outcome.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20at%20this%20point%20how%20withholding%20pay%20from%20a%20servicer%20would%20impact%20its%20operations%2C%20and%20whether%20the%20impact%20would%20trickle%20down%20to%20borrowers.%20Scott%20Buchanan%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Student%20Loan%20Servicing%20Alliance%20%E2%80%94%20a%20group%20that%20represents%20federal%20servicers%20%E2%80%94%20told%20Insider%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bdoesn't%20understand%20the%20logic%26quot%3B%20of%20withholding%20MOHELA's%20pay%20at%20a%20time%20when%20resources%20are%20already%20strained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20cut%20millions%20of%20dollars%20out%20of%20someone's%20budget%2C%20there%20will%20be%20consequences%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20either%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20add%20more%20reps%20that%20they%20wanted%20to%20do%2C%20have%20to%20cut%20staff%20time%2C%20you%20know%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20make%20cuts%2C%20and%20those%20cuts%20are%20going%20to%20impact%20borrowers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Republicans%20holding%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20House%2C%20it's%20unlikely%20Federal%20Student%20Aid%20will%20see%20boosted%20funding%20in%20the%20upcoming%20year.%20Biden's%20budget%20request%20included%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-bidens-budget-proposal-support-return-to-repayment-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%242.7%20billion%20in%20funding%20for%20FSA%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20%24620%20million%20increase%20from%20the%202023%20level%20%E2%80%94%20but%20Republicans%20on%20the%20House%20Appropriations%20Committee%20released%20a%20funding%20bill%20that%20would%20fund%20FSA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-repayment-more-hurdles-gop-budget-cut-proposal-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24265%20million%20below%20its%20current%20level.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJared%20Bass%2C%20senior%20vice%20president%20for%20the%20Education%20department%20at%20the%20think%20tank%20Center%20for%20American%20Progress%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20federal%20government%20needs%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20type%20of%20servicing%20it%20wants%20to%20see.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20certainly%20believe%20that%20we%20should%20hold%20servicers%20to%20a%20standard%20and%20make%20sure%20that%20they're%20providing%20quality%20services%2C%26quot%3B%20Bass%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20if%20there's%20only%20so%20much%20money%20that%20the%20federal%20government%20is%20going%20to%20pay%20the%20servicer%2C%20that%20also%20is%20going%20to%20impact%20the%20quality%20of%20work%20that%20the%20servicer%20can%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20bolstering%20oversight%20over%20servicers%20by%20withholding%20their%20pay%2C%20Bass%20said%2C%20it's%20%26quot%3Ba%20catch%2022.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20quality%20servicing%2C%20we%20have%20to%20hold%20people%20accountable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we%20also%20want%20servicing%20and%20that%20costs%20money%20since%20we%20want%20people%20to%20do%20the%20job%20well.%20I%20think%20it's%20just%20darned%20if%20you%20do%2C%20darned%20if%20you%20don't.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'What%20happens%20to%20servicing%20should%20be%20a%20main%20concern%20for%20everyone'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Federal%20Student%20Aid%20internal%20memo%20outlined%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcan-student-loan-borrowers-file-lawsuit-servicer-mohela-fsa-memo-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20wide%20range%20of%20problems%20borrowers%20have%20been%20facing%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20they%20entered%20repayment.%20For%20example%2C%2078%2C000%20borrowers%20faced%20incorrect%20monthly%20bills%20when%20converting%20to%20the%20new%20income-driven%20repayment%20plan%2C%20and%20153%2C000%20borrowers%20did%20not%20receive%20any%20information%20on%20their%20monthly%20payments%20until%20after%20they%20became%20due.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Education%20Department%20is%20working%20on%20remedying%20those%20errors%20and%20has%20instructed%20servicers%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmohela-student-loan-borrowers-missed-payments-forbearance-debt-education-department-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplace%20all%20impacted%20borrowers%20on%20administrative%20forbearance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20without%20any%20interest%20accrual%2C%20and%20vowed%20to%20continue%20oversight%20over%20servicers%20as%20repayment%20progresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuchanan%20noted%20that%20he's%20still%20determining%20how%20exactly%20withholding%20pay%20would%20impact%20operations%20and%20added%20that%20he's%20%26quot%3Bnot%20making%20any%20excuses%20for%20the%20mistakes%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20incentive%20is%20to%20get%20this%20thing%20right%2C%20but%20when%20you're%20resource-%20constrained%2C%20this%20is%20what%20happens%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20an%20issue%20only%20Congress%20can%20solve.%20Lawmakers%20need%20to%20pass%20government%20funding%20legislation%20before%20a%20government%20shutdown%20after%20November%2017%2C%20and%20Bass%20said%20it'll%20be%20critical%20to%20see%20how%20appropriations%20bills%20take%20into%20account%20student%20aid%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20very%20significant%20cut%20to%20student-loan%20servicing%20in%20that%20bill%2C%20and%20so%20what%20happens%20to%20that%20account%2C%20what%20happens%20to%20servicing%2C%20should%20be%20a%20main%20concern%20for%20everyone%2C%20not%20just%20to%20those%20who%20have%20student%20loans%2C%26quot%3B%20Bass%20said.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20when%20we%20care%20about%20government%20systems%2C%20when%20we%20care%20about%20social%20trust%20and%20trust%20in%20government%2C%20we%20should%20be%20thinking%20about%20institutions%20and%20how%20we%20are%20maintaining%20them%2C%20how%20we%20are%20making%20sure%20that%20they%20thrive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-companies-mohela-punished-borrowers-repayment-servicer-errors-education-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699091521000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65439b7d36d588dc55c9075a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-companies-mohela-punished-borrowers-repayment-servicer-errors-education-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Student-loan%20company%20MOHELA%20lost%20%247%20million%20in%20pay%2C%20the%20first%20servicer%20to%20get%20punished%20for%20repayment%20errors.%20But%20it%20might%20not%20fully%20help%20borrowers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asheffey%40businessinsider.com%20(Ayelet%20Sheffey)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-companies-mohela-punished-borrowers-repayment-servicer-errors-education-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Byju's%20core%20business%20reports%202.3x%20revenue%20growth%2C%20Rs%202253%20crore%20loss%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699090833000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-07%2F11%2Ffull%2F1689067015-2953.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fbyju-s-core-business-reports-2-3x-revenue-growth-rs-2253-crore-loss-123110400461_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20financials%20revealed%20by%20Byju's%20are%20based%20on%20an%20'unqualified%20FY22%20audit'%20and%20it%20will%20file%20the%20financials%20with%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Corporate%20Affairs%20(MCA)%20in%20the%20next%20few%20weeks%2C%20according%20to%20the%20sources%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%2