real%20and%20scientific%20director%20at%20the%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20Institute%20in%20Quebec.%20Bengio%20was%20among%20a%20trio%20of%20computer%20scientists%20whose%20insights%20and%20persistence%20were%20rewarded%20Wednesday%2C%20March%2026%2C%202019%2C%20with%20the%20Turing%20Award%2C%20an%20honor%20that%20has%20become%20known%20as%20technology%20industry%E2%80%99s%20version%20of%20the%20Nobel%20Prize.%20It%20comes%20with%20a%20%241%20million%20prize%20funded%20by%20Google%2C%20a%20company%20where%20AI%20has%20become%20part%20of%20its%20DNA.%20(Maryse%20Boyce%2FMila%20via%20AP)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5c9b61482730ca2efb6f8890%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYoshua%20Bengio%20is%20a%20Turing%20Award-winning%20computer%20scientist.%3Cp%3EAssociated%20Press%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAn%20AI%20godfather%20says%20we%20should%20all%20be%20worried%20about%20the%20concentration%20of%20power%20in%20the%20AI%20sector.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EYoshua%20Bengio%20said%20the%20potential%20issue%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bnumber%20two%20problem%26quot%3B%20after%20existential%20risks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBengio%20said%20the%20control%20of%20powerful%20AI%20systems%20was%20a%20central%20question%20for%20democracy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20concentration%20of%20power%20in%20the%20AI%20arena%20is%20one%20of%20the%20main%20risks%20facing%20the%20industry%2C%20an%20AI%20godfather%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ai-chief-yoshua-bengio-risk-yann-lecun-ai-godfather-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYoshua%20Bengio%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20Turing%20Award-winning%20Canadian%20computer%20scientist%2C%20told%20Insider%20the%20potential%20for%20the%20AI%20sector%20to%20be%20controlled%20by%20a%20few%20companies%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bnumber%20two%20problem%26quot%3B%20behind%20the%20existential%20risks%20posed%20by%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20on%20a%20trajectory%20to%20build%20more%20and%20more%20powerful%20systems%20and%20the%20central%20question%20for%20democracy%20is%20who%20controls%20these%20systems%20%E2%80%93%20is%20there%20a%20risk%20of%20excessive%20concentration%20of%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20important%20questions%20I've%20been%20thinking%20about%20for%20years%20but%20the%20arrival%20of%20ChatGPT%20and%20these%20systems%20made%20me%20worry%20even%20more%20about%20the%20concentration%20of%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20Bengio%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAddressing%20concerns%20raised%20by%20fellow%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-and-demis-hassabis-just-want-to-control-ai-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20pioneer%20Yann%20LeCun%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Bengio%20said%20he%20disagreed%20with%20LeCun's%20suggestion%20that%20prominent%20tech%20leaders%20including%20OpenAI's%20Sam%20Altman%20were%20trying%20to%20control%20the%20sector%20by%20pushing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-destroying-humanity-big-con-tech-existential-risks-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efor%20stronger%20regulation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20LeCun%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fylecun%2Fstatus%2F1718670073391378694%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccused%20AI%20founders%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20as%20DeepMind's%20Demis%20Hassabis%20and%20Anthropic's%20Dario%20Amodei%20of%20attempting%20to%20perform%20a%20%26quot%3Bregulatory%20capture%20of%20the%20AI%20industry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20should%20avoid%20the%20situation%20where%20the%20rules%20are%20written%20by%20the%20companies%20%E2%80%93%20that's%20obvious%2C%26quot%3B%20Bengio%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20this%20whole%20discussion%20about%20regulatory%20capture%20I%20think%20it's%20just%20