nd%20former%20food%20minister%20Jyoti%20Priya%20Mallick%2C%20an%20old%20loyalist%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20chief.%20Mallick%20is%20the%20top%20leader%20from%20North%2024-Parganas%2C%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20most-populous%20district%20with%20five%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMamataBanerjeeOfficial%2Fvideos%2F1407369126658789%5C%22%3E34-minute%20monologue%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Banerjee%20came%20out%20strongly%20in%20Mallick%E2%80%99s%20support%20and%20blasted%20the%20Modi%20government%20for%20%E2%80%9Charassing%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cterrorising%E2%80%9D%20opposition%20leaders%2C%20but%20made%20no%20mention%20of%20or%20reference%20to%20Moitra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20leaders%20in%20the%20districts%20were%20all%20busy%20managing%20the%20local%20Durga%20puja%20carnivals.%20Today%2C%20at%20the%20crack%20of%20dawn%2C%20people%20came%20to%20Balu%E2%80%99s%20(as%20Mallick%20is%20known)%20house%20and%20found%20the%20ED%20was%20conducting%20a%20raid.%20If%20they%20are%20to%20raid%20every%20minister%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20then%20what%20is%20left%20of%20the%20(state)%20government%3F%20If%20the%20BJP%20believes%20they%20can%20silence%20everyone%20this%20way%E2%80%A6%20this%20is%20a%20dirty%20game%20and%20they%20are%20pathological%20liars%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBalu%20has%20high%20blood%20sugar%20and%20has%20not%20been%20well.%20If%20he%20dies%2C%20we%20will%20have%20to%20lodge%20police%20cases%20against%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20ED%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F04122300%2FFszZVD9aQAYfcvn.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F