ire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F07142954%2FFlag-Of-Palestine-Arab-Man-Waving-1081797.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0An%20Israeli%20air%20strike%20on%20Friday%2C%20November%203%2C%20hit%20a%20convoy%20of%20ambulances%20near%20the%20al-Shifa%20Hospital%20in%20Gaza%2C%20killing%20at%20least%2015%20people%20and%20injuring%20more%20than%2050%2C%20according%20to%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F11%2F3%2Fseveral-killled-in-israeli-attack-on-ambulance-convoy-gaza-health-ministry%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAl%20Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20convoy%20was%20transporting%20critically%20wounded%20patients%20from%20the%20Al-Shifa%20Hospital%20to%20the%20Rafah%20border%20crossing%20with%20Egypt%20when%20it%20was%20struck.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUN%20secretary-general%20Antonio%20Guterres%20said%20he%20was%20%E2%80%9Chorrified%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20strike%20adding%20that%20the%20conflict%20%E2%80%9Cmust%20stop%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20horrified%20by%20the%20reported%20attack%20in%20Gaza%20on%20an%20ambulance%20convoy%20outside%20Al%20Shifa%20hospital.%20The%20images%20of%20bodies%20strewn%20on%20the%20street%20outside%20the%20hospital%20are%20harrowing%2C%E2%80%9D%20Guterres%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20humanitarian%20situation%20in%20Gaza%20was%20%E2%80%9Chorrific%E2%80%9D%20and%20reiterated%20his%20call%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20and%20the%20release%20of%20hostages%20taken%20by%20Hamas%20in%20its%20initial%20attack%20on%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWorld%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%20director-general%20Tedros%20Adhanom%20Ghebreyesus%20also%20expressed%20utter%20shock%20at%20the%20reports.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CWe%20reiterate%2C%20patients%2C%20health%20workers%2C%20facilities%2C%20and%20ambulances%20must%20be%20protected%20at%20all%20times%2C%20always%2C%E2%80%9D%20Adhanom%20Ghebreyesus%20said%20in%20on%20X%20(formerl