Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20US%20Geological%20Survey%2C%20the%20earthquake%20had%20a%20preliminary%20magnitude%20of%205.6%20and%20occurred%20at%20a%20depth%20of%2017.9%20kilometres%20(11.1%20miles).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20German%20Research%20Center%20for%20Geosciences%20(GFZ)%20pegged%20the%20earthquake%20at%20a%20magnitude%20of%206.2%20and%20a%20depth%20of%2010%20kilometres%20(6.2%20miles).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecurity%20forces%20mobilized%20to%20help%20rescue%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENepalese%20Prime%20Minister%20Pushpa%20Kamal%20expressed%20%E2%80%9Chis%20deep%20sorrow%20over%20the%20human%20and%20physical%20damage%20caused%20by%20the%20earthquake.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20deployed%20security%20forces%20to%20assist%20in%C2%A0the%C2%A0rescue%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20information%20that%20there%20have%20been%20human%20and%20physical%20damages%20in%20two%20districts%20because%20of%20the%20quake%2C%20and%20security%20forces%20have%20been%20mobilized%20for%20rescue%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Home%20Ministry%20spokesman%20Narayan%20Prasad%20Bhattarai.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETremors%20were%20felt%20as%20far%20away%20as%20New%20Delhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20tremors%20were%20felt%20as%20far%20as%20New%20Delhi%2C%20the%20capital%20of%20India.%C2%A0Videos%20on%20the%20social%20media%20platform%20X%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter%2C%20showed%20people%20running%20into%20the%20streets%20as%20some%20buildings%20were%20evacuated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMountainous%20Nepal%20is%20prone%20to%20earthquakes.%20The%20Himalayan%20region%2C%20where%20Nepal%20is%20located%2C%20is%20extremely%20active%20geologically.%20The%20Indian%20continental%20plate%20is%20shifting%20beneath%20the%20Eurasian%20plate%20at%20a%20rate%20of%20about%20two%20centimetres%20per%20year%2C%20resulting%20in%20frequent%20earthquakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ffear-and-shock-