les%20in%20just%20three%20weeks%20of%20assaults%20as%20Ukraine%20lost%20over%20several%20months%20of%20fighting%20in%20the%20south.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Russian%20offensive%20to%20capture%20a%20small%2C%20ruined%20town%20in%20eastern%20Ukraine%20has%20been%20a%20costly%20battle.%20In%20vehicle%20losses%2C%20the%20Russian%20assault%20force%20has%20lost%20in%20just%20three%20weeks%20what%20Ukrainian%20troops%20lost%20over%20several%20months%20of%20intense%20fighting%20in%20the%20south.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Russia%20launched%20a%20renewed%20offensive%20near%20Avdiivka%2C%20a%20small%20town%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20occupied%20Donetsk.%20Since%20the%20fighting%20began%2C%20its%20forces%20have%20made%20some%20advances%20and%20have%20effectively%20surrounded%20a%20pocket%20of%20Ukrainian%20defenders.%20But%20that%20progress%20has%20come%20at%20a%20high%20cost%20for%20Russia%2C%20both%20in%20troops%20and%20vehicles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20October%209%2C%20the%20Russian%20assault%20forces%20have%20suffered%20at%20least%20197%20damaged%20and%20destroyed%20vehicles%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Wednesday%20Institute%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20War%2C%20a%20Washington%20DC-based%20think%20tank%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.understandingwar.org%2Fbackgrounder%2Frussian-offensive-campaign-assessment-november-1-2023-0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20citing%20open-source%20geolocation%20project%20GeoConfirmed.%2099%20vehicles%20were%20lost%20in%20the%20first%20wave%20of%20assaults%20between%20October%209%20and%2013%2C%20and%20another%2094%20were%20lost%20between%20October%2014%20and%2023.%20Since%20then%2C%20four%20additional%20vehicles%20have%20been%20confirmed%20lost.%20Another%2018%20are%20considered%20potentially%20wrecked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGeoConfirmed%20characterized%20the%20Russian%20effort%20near%20Avdiivka%20as%20the%20costliest%20Russian%20effort%20thus%20far%20in%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%26quot%3B%20ISW%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20figures%20are%20staggering%2C%20especially%20when%20compared%20to%20Ukraine's%20losses%20over%20months%20along%20another%20part%20of%20the%20front%20line%20in%20the%20south%20near%20Zaporizhzhia%2C%20where%20Ukrainian%20forces%20have%20been%20pushing%20against%20fortified%20Russian%20defenses%20as%20part%20of%20the%20ongoing%20counteroffensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Ukrainians%20lost%20a%20little%20above%20200%20vehicles%2C%20that%20we%20can%20observe%20and%20confirm%2C%20in%20southern%20Ukraine%20in%20Zaporizhzhia%20over%20the%20course%20of%20four%20or%20five%20months%20of%20operation%2C%26quot%3B%20George%20Barros%2C%20the%20geospatial-intelligence%20team%20lead%20and%20a%20Russia%20analyst%20at%20ISW%2C%20told%20Insider.%C2%A0It%20took%20Russia%20roughly%20three%20weeks%20fighting%20for%20Avdiivka%20to%20do%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20comparison%20paints%20a%20sobering%20picture%20of%20the%20costs%20of%20the%20assault%20for%20Russia.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can%20conclude%20now%20that%20this%20is%20by%20far%20the%20most%20costly%20Russian%20assault%20during%20three%20weeks%20for%20one%20city%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20Barros%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20an%20undertaking%20that%20lasted%20three%20weeks%20just%20for%20one%20town%2C%20this%20is%20the%20most%20costly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ukrainian%20army%20soldiers%20of%20the%2022nd%20brigade%20during%20tank%20training%20as%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%20continues%20in%20Donetsk%20Oblast%2C%20Ukraine%20on%20October%2029%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654548ec3cc84b4dfafc4d85%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkrainian%20army%20soldiers%20of%20the%2022nd%20brigade%20during%20tank%20training%20as%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%20continues%20in%20D