20and%20strike(s)%20in%20terms%20of%20rule%20mentioned%20supra%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20GAD%20circular%20(No.%20GAD-ADM0III%2F158%2F2023-09-GAD)%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERule%20(ii)%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20employee%20conduct%20rules%20bars%20the%20government%20employees%20from%20organising%20or%20participating%20in%20%E2%80%9Cany%20form%20of%20strike%20in%20connection%20with%20their%20service%20matter%20or%20the%20service%20matter%20of%20other%20government%20employee%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTherefore%2C%20all%20Administrative%20Secretaries%20are%20requested%20to%20circulate%20these%20instructions%20to%20employees%20in%20their%20respective%20Department(s)%20to%20desist%20from%20all%20such%20uncalled%20for%20demonstrations%20and%20strikes%3A%20an%20act%20of%20serious%20indiscipline%20and%20misconduct%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20GAD%20circular%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20circular%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20hundreds%20of%20employees%20have%20been%20sacked%20by%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20administration%20on%20allegedly%20arbitrary%20grounds%20while%20close%20to%2050%20employees%20have%20been%20terminated%20in%20the%20last%20four%20years%20on%20charges%20of%20being%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Csecurity%20of%20the%20state.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20there%20are%20more%20than%20five%20lakh%20employees%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20The%20number%20of%20contractual%20employees%20is%20close%20to%20one%20lakh%20who%20are%20hired%20by%20various%20departments%20against%20existing%20vacancies%20without%20giving%20them%20employment%20benefits%20of%20permanent%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20weeks%20and%20months%2C%20aggrieved%20employees%2C%20including%20those%20working%20with%20the%20central%20government%20departments%2C%20have%20been%20hitting%20the%20streets%20in%20bouts%20across%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20to%20seek%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20government%20in%20addressing%20their%20employment%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20contractual%20employees%20hired%20for%20the%20central%20government%20schemes%20such%20as%20National%20Health%20Mission%2C%20MNREGA%2C%20and%20Gram%20Rozgar%20Sevak%20have%20taken%20out%20their%20anger%20against%20the%20government%20on%20the%20streets%2C%20while%20demanding%20an%20increase%20in%20their%20wages%20and%20regularisation%20of%20their%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20October%2030%2C%20dozens%20of%20employees%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Road%20Transport%20Corporation%20staged%20a%20protest%20at%20Press%20Enclave%20in%20Srinagar%E2%80%99s%20Lal%20Chowk%20to%20demand%20the%20resolution%20of%20their%20demands%2C%20including%20regular%20employment%20benefits%2C%20regularisation%2C%20and%20implementation%20of%20the%20Minimum%20Wages%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20by%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20Srinagar%E2%80%99s%20Press%20Enclave%20worked%20as%20an%20ideal%20interface%20of%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20government%20with%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPolitical%20parties%2C%20business%20leaders%2C%20social%20activists%2C%20students%2C%20or%20any%20aggrieved%20person%20from%20any%20part%20of%20Kashmir%20would%20surface%20at%20the%20Press%20Enclave%20and%20stage%20protest%20or%20demonstration%20there%20while%20media%20persons%2C%20who%20hover%20around%20in%20the%20area%2C%20brought%20it%20to%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20downgrading%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20into%20two%20Union%20territories%2C%20the%20Press%20Enclave%20fell%20silent%20as%20authorities%20cracked%20down%20on%20protesters%20across%20the%20Valley.%20In%20recent%20months%2C%20however%2C%20the%20former%20hub%20of%20journalists%2C%20which%20now%20also%20houses%20the%20office%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20counterterrorism%20unit%2C%20had%20again%20turned%20into%20a%20happening%20place%20with%20several%20protests%20organised%20here%20in%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20thousands%20of%20employees%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20Power%20Department%20went%20on%20a%20strike%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20plunging%20the%20union%20territory%20into%20darkness%20amid%20reports%20that%20the%20government%20was%20planning%20to%20privatise%20the%20department%20and%20merge%20it%20with%20the%20Power%20Grid%20Corporation%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20employees%20later%20called%20off%20the%20strike%20after%20the%20administration%20assured%20them%20that%20the%20plan%20had%20been%20put%20on%20hold.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20Kashmiri%20Pandit%20employees%20had%20gone%20on%20strike%20for%20months%20following%20a%20spate%20of%20targeted%20killings%20of%20the%20minority%20Hindus%20and%20migrant%20workers%20by%20militants%20in%202021%2C%20which%20prompted%20many%20of%20them%20to%20leave%20the%20Valley.%20The%20strike%20was%20called%20off%20after%20nearly%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699033943000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2F08170336%2FUntitled-design-2021-05-08T170303.358-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjk-admin-orders-employees-to-stay-away-from-strikes-warns-of-strict-disciplinary-action%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20recent%20weeks%20and%20months%2C%20aggrieved%20employees%20have%20been%20hitting%20the%20streets%20across%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20to%20seek%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20government%20in%20addressing%20their%20employment%20matters.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjk-admin-orders-employees-to-stay-away-from-strikes-warns-of-strict-disciplinary-action%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20How%20UAW's%20drive%20to%20'end%20tiers'%20will%20change%20GM%20Detroit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699033521000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22