0to%20combating%20environmental%20issues%20and%20will%20always%20place%20the%20interest%20of%20our%20fans%20and%20stakeholders%20at%20the%20forefront%E2%80%9D%2C%20in%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20words.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20on%20November%201%2C%20said%20it%20is%20important%20that%20future%20generations%20be%20able%20to%20live%20without%20fear.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20an%20ideal%20world%2C%20you%20do%20not%20want%20a%20situation%20like%20this%20but%20I%20am%20pretty%20sure%20that%20the%20concerned%20people%20are%20taking%20the%20necessary%20steps%20to%20avoid%20this%20kind%20of%20situation%2C%E2%80%9D%20ESPNCricInfo%20quoted%20Sharma%20as%20saying%20before%20India%E2%80%99s%20World%20Cup%20match%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%20in%20Mumbai.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20ideal%20and%20everyone%20knows%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CLooking%20at%20our%20future%20generations%2C%20your%20kids%2C%20my%20kid%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sharma%20said.%20%E2%80%9CObviously%20it%20is%20important%20that%20they%20get%20to%20live%20without%20any%20fear.%20Every%20time%20I%20get%20to%20speak%20outside%20of%20cricket%2C%20or%20not%20discussing%20cricket%2C%20I%20always%20talk%20about%20this.%20We%20have%20to%20look%20after%20our%20future%20generations.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699029690000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F13184606%2FPollution.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fdelhi-air-quality-in-severe-category-no-respite-from-pollution-in-sight%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bangladesh%20cricket%20team%20cancelled%20its%20training%20session%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20on%20Friday%2C%20citing%20the%20air%20quality.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fdelhi-air-quality-in-