%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwhats-russia-doing-when-the-world-is-not-looking-12999490%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwhats-russia-doing-when-the-world-is-not-looking-12999490%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Telangana%20Polls%3A%20Congress%20Ups%20the%20Ante%20Against%20BRS%20Over%20Damage%20to%20Kaleshwaram%20Project%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F03161334%2FThe-Wire-64.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHyderabad%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20sinking%20of%20a%20couple%20of%20piers%20of%20a%20barrage%20of%20the%20Kaleshwaram%20project%20%E2%80%93%20touted%20as%20the%20biggest%20lift%20irrigation%20project%20in%20the%20world%2C%20across%20river%20Godavari%20in%20the%20Bhoopalpally%20district%20of%20Telangana%20%E2%80%93%20has%20given%20the%20Congress%20party%20a%20point%20of%20attack%20on%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20ahead%20of%20assembly%20polls%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20piers%20at%20the%20Medigadda%20barrage%20sank%20on%20October%2021.%20But%2C%20on%20November%201%2C%20another%20barrage%20of%20the%20same%20project%20downstream%20of%20the%20river%20at%20Annaram%20village%20showed%20bubbles%2C%20reflecting%20seepage%20of%20water%20underneath%20the%20raft%20foundation%20of%20two%20more%20piers.%20This%20led%20to%20the%20Congress%20pressing%20the%20panic%20button.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ENational%20Dam%20safety%20Authority%20has%20given%20its%20report%20on%20Kaleshwaram%20project%E2%80%99s%20sinking%20of%20piers%20at%20Medigadda%20barrage%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReport%20says%20%E2%80%93%20Sinking%20of%20piers%20is%20a%20result%20of%20a%20combination%20of%20issues%20related%20to%20planning%2C%20design%2C%20quality%20control%2C%20and%20operation%20and%20maintenance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrimary%20cause%20of%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FmbB3NHiCV3%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FmbB3NHiCV3%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Naveena%20(%40TheNaveena)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTheNaveena%2Fstatus%2F1720342681929576926%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%203%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20was%20supposed%20to%20return%20to%20Delhi%20after%20two%20days%20of%20election%20campaign%20in%20the%20state%20on%20Wednesday%20evening%2C%20called%20off%20his%20departure%20and%20rushed%20to%20Medigadda%20to%20see%20the%20site%20early%20on%20the%20next%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStrangely%2C%20the%20BRS%20government%20which%20had%20always%20denied%20permission%20to%20the%20Congress%20party%20to%20visit%20projects%20or%20even%20hold%20demonstrations%20highlighting%20alleged%20lapses%2C%20facilitated%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20visit%20by%20constructing%20a%20helipad%20on%20payment%20of%20cost%20by%20the%20party.%20He%20flew%20in%20by%20helicopter%2C%20addressed%20a%20public%20meeting%20nearby%2C%20and%20then%20left%20for%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20upped%20the%20ante%20against%20the%20government%20over%20the%20sinking%20of%20piers%2C%20by%20saying%20that%20the%20Kaleswaram%20project%20had%20become%20an%20ATM%20for%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrashekhar%20Rao%20(KCR).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20president%20J.P.%20Nadda%20initially%20and%20later%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20who%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fhyderabad%2Ftelangana-congress-leaders-urge-amit-shah-to-take-action-against-kcr-family%2Farticleshow%2F93714080.cms%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20their%20public%20meetings%20last%20year%20that%20made%20this%20claim%2C%20noting%20there%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cscam%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20Congress%20party%20and%20the%20BJP%20have%2C%20at%20regular%20intervals%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20attacked%20the%20BRS%20government%20for%20the%20project%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20faulty%20design%20and%20escalating%20its%20cost%20from%20Rs%2040%2C000%20crore%20when%20it%20was%20conceived%20to%20Rs%201.40%20lakh%20crore%20now%2C%20with%20some%20more%20work%20pending.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20set%20up%20replicas%20of%20ATMs%2C%20calling%20them%20%E2%80%98Kaleshwaram%20ATMs%E2%80%99%2C%20to%20symbolically%20shed%20light%20on%20the%20alleged%20scam%20in%20some%20places.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20shown%20one%20such%20ATM%20at%20Shadnagar%20during%20his%20campaign.%20They%20say%3A%20%E2%80%9CKaleshwaram%20ATM.%20This%20century%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20scam%20(Rs%201%20lakh%20crore).%20KCR%20%3D%20Kaleshwaram%20Corruption%20Rao.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F03161421%2FF93FugdWwAAJ_0E.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221023%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F03161421%2FF93FugdWwAAJ_0E.jpg%201023w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F03161421%2FF93FugdWwAAJ_0E-300x185.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683374%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECongress%20leaders%20show%20a%20replica%20of%20ATM%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%98Kaleshwaram%20ATM%E2%80%99%2C%20to%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20in%20Shadnagar%2C%20Telangana.%20Photo%3A%20X%20(Twitter)%2F%40revanth_anumula%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnion%20tourism%20minister%20and%20BJP%20state%20president%20G.%20Kishan%20Reddy%20alerted%20the%20Union%20water%20resources%20minister%20Gajendra%20Singh%20Shekhawat%20about%20the%20damage%20at%20Medigadda%20as%20soon%20as%20it%20came%20to%20light.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20a%20six-member%20team%20of%20the%20National%20Dam%20Safety%20Authority%2C%20led%20by%20its%20chairman%20Anil%20Jain%2C%20was%20constituted%20to%20study%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20carried%20out%20a%20preliminary%20investigation%20at%20the%20site%20and%20suggested%20a%20geological%20investigation%20after%20evacuating%20water%20from%20the%20reservoir%2C%20said%20Sridhar%20Deshpande%2C%20an%20officer%20on%20special%20duty%20(OSD)%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20who%20also%20held%20the%20irrigation%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDeshpande%20said%20the%20initial%20investigation%20revealed%20that%20only%20one%20pier%20caved%20in%20due%20to%20hollowness%20caused%20by%20sand%20erosion%20under%20its%20raft%20foundation.%20A%20geological%20investigation%20will%20be%20done%20to%20know%20the%20exact%20cause%20after%20dewatering%20the%20area%20and%20constructing%20a%20cofferdam.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20the%20sinking%20of%20one%20pier%20had%20a%20cascading%20effect%20on%20adjacent%20piers%20and%20resulted%20in%20cracks%20of%20slabs%20in%20piers%20on%20either%20side%20of%20the%20damaged%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20reclamation%20steps%20will%20be%20taken%20in%20all%20eight%20blocks%20accommodating%20the%20piers%20after%20the%20geological%20survey.%C2%A0He%20recalled%20that%20the%20barrage%20withstood%20all%20floods%2C%20including%20the%20biggest%20ever%20in%20the%20river%20last%20year%2C%20since%20its%20commissioning%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERegarding%20the%20seepage%20of%20water%20at%20pillars%20in%20Annaram%2C%20Deshpande%20said%20it%20was%20a%20routine%20discharge%20of%20water%20from%20the%20permeable%20raft%20foundation.%20It%20was%20a%20pressure%20relief%20arrangement%20made%20as%20a%20built-in%20mechanism%20with%20sand%20filters.%20Whether%20the%20water%20was%20released%20within%20the%20permissible%20limit%20or%20not%20was%20to%20be%20seen.%20Also%2C%20it%20should%20be%20ensured%20that%20the%20water%20does%20not%20carry%20soil%20particles%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20irrigation%20department%20is%20evacuating%20about%2010%20tmcft%20of%20water%20by%20opening%20all%2085%20gates%20of%20the%20Medigadda%20barrage%20to%20construct%20the%20cofferdam%20and%20prevent%20fresh%20inflows%20in%20the%20river.%20It%20has%20also%20mobilised%20hundreds%20of%20sandbags%20and%20stones%20to%20close%20the%20affected%20points%20in%20the%20Annaram%20barrage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESenior%20Congress%20leader%20and%20former%20Maharashtra%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Chavan%20who%20was%20in%20Hyderabad%20on%20Thursday%20alleged%20at%20a%20media%20conference%20that%20Rs.%2097%2C449%20crore%20belonging%20to%20state%20public%20sector%20undertakings%20was%20spent%20on%20the%20Kaleshwaram%20project%20so%20far.%20The%20burden%20on%20people%20due%20to%20debt%20servicing%20will%20go%20up%20to%20Rs%2025%2C109%20crore%20by%202040%2C%20Chavan%20claimed.%20There%20was%20a%20250%25%20hike%20in%20project%20cost%20due%20to%20price%20escalation.%20%E2%80%9CWhere%20did%20all%20the%20money%20go%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBRS%20minister%20K.T.%20Rama%20Rao%20had%20earlier%20said%20there%20would%20be%20no%20burden%20on%20the%20state%20exchequer%20due%20to%20the%20sinking%20of%20piers%20as%20the%20barrage%20was%20constructed%20by%20L%26amp%3BT%20under%20a%20defect%20liability%20period%20of%20five%20years.%20Seven%20ultra-critical%20pumps%20at%20the%20pumping%20station%20at%20Medigadda%20were%20submerged%20during%20heavy%20floods%20last%20year.%20The%20contracting%20agency%20undertook%20the%20repair%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699020034000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F03161334%2FThe-Wire-64.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2F