%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fombirlakota%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40ombirlakota%3C%2Fa%3E%20ji%20for%20reinstating%20Mohammed%20Faizal%20PP%20as%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%2C%20following%20the%20directions%20of%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20people%20of%20his%20Lakshadweep%20Parliamentary%20Constituency%20can%20finally%20breathe%20a%20sigh%20of%20relief%2C%20knowing%20that%20their%20elected%20representative%20is%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FW1a6e1TXGw%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FW1a6e1TXGw%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F63pPNmogPd%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F63pPNmogPd%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Supriya%20Sule%20(%40supriya_sule)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsupriya_sule%2Fstatus%2F1720039011815989689%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%202%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20November%201%2C%20NCP%20leader%20Supriya%20Sule%20wrote%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Prakash%20Birla%2C%20seeking%20Faizal%E2%80%99s%20reinstatement%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20it%20had%20been%2023%20days%20since%20the%20apex%20court%20ordered%20his%20reinstatement%2C%3Cem%3E%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Flakshadweep-lok-sabha-mp-pp-mohammed-faizal-reinstated-for-second-time%2Farticleshow%2F104927241.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECiting%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20order%2C%20she%20said%20that%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Secretariat%E2%80%99s%20failure%20to%20act%20on%20the%20apex%20court%E2%80%99s%20directions%20was%20%E2%80%9Cdepriving%20Lakshadweep%20of%20its%20rightful%20representation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFaizal%20was%20first%20disqualified%20as%20an%20MP%20on%20January%2011%2C%20following%20his%20sentencing%20to%2010%20years%E2%80%99%20imprisonment%20and%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%20by