Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20current%20points%20table%2C%20South%20Africa%20and%20India%20hold%20the%20top%20two%20places%20with%2012%20points%20each.%20New%20Zealand%20are%20fourth%20(8%20points%2C%207%20matches%2C%20NRR%20%2B0.484)%20while%20Australia%20are%20third%20(8%20points%2C%206%20matches%2C%20NRR%20%2B0.970).%20Pakistan%20are%20placed%20fifth%20(6%20points%2C%207%20games%2C%20NRR%20-0.024)%20and%20Afghanistan%20are%20sixth%20(6%20points%2C%206%20matches%2C%20NRR%20-0.718).%20With%20New%20Zealand's%20defeat%2C%20they%20are%20within%20touching%20distance%20of%20the%20next%20three%20teams%20in%20the%20points%20table.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPakistan's%20next%20two%20matches%20are%20against%20New%20Zealand%20and%20England.%20If%20they%20can%20win%20those%20and%20other%20teams'%20results%20go%20their%20way%2C%20the%20side%20may%20have%20an%20outside%20chance%20of%20making%20it%20to%20the%20last%20four.%20However%2C%20Afghanistan%20and%207th-placed%20Sri%20Lanka%20(4%20points%2C%206%20matches%2C%20NRR%20-0.275)%20are%20also%20in%20contention.%20Afghanistan%20next%20face%20Netherlands%2C%20Australia%20and%20South%20Africa.%20Sri%20Lanka%20next%20face%20India%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20New%20Zealand.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20South%20Africa's%20in-form%20opener%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Quinton%20de%20Kock%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1577-quinton-de-kock-playerprofile%5C%22%3EQuinton%20de%20Kock%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday%20slammed%20his%20fourth%20hundred%20of%20the%20ICC%20World%20Cup%202023%20and%20became%20the%20first%20batter%20from%20his%20country%20to%20cross%20the%20500-run%20mark%20in%20a%20World%20Cup%20edition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fdjeuh2d_points_625x300_01_November_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3