charged%20with%20menacing%20and%20second-degree%20endangering%20the%20welfare%20of%20a%20child%2C%20Nassau%20County%20police%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20began%20when%20a%20mother%20drove%20her%20daughter%2C%20two%20sons%2C%20and%20a%20nephew%20to%20a%20nearby%20residence%20to%20drop%20off%20a%20goody%20bag.%20Her%2010-year-old%20daughter%20and%206-year-old%20son%20rang%20the%20doorbell%20and%20dropped%20off%20a%20Halloween%20goody%20bag%20on%20the%20porch%20for%20the%20girl's%20friend.%20However%2C%20when%20the%20children%20returned%20to%20the%20car%2C%20the%20girl%20told%20her%20mother%20the%20address%20may%20have%20been%20incorrect%2C%20so%20they%20drove%20back%2C%20and%20the%20boy%20went%20to%20the%20porch%20to%20get%20the%20bag%20full%20of%20candy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20when%20the%20man%20opened%20the%20door%20and%20pointed%20a%20handgun%20at%20the%20boy's%20head%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Fus-news%2Fman-allegedly-points-gun-6-year-old-left-halloween-goody-bag-wrong-hou-rcna123025%5C%22%3Eoutlet%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%20The%20Nassau%20County%20Police%20Department%20were%20immediately%20notified%20of%20the%20incident%20and%20the%2043-year-old%20suspect%20was%20arrested.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Wen's%20attorney%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20his%20client%20is%20presumed%20innocent.%20%26quot%3BThese%20are%20just%20allegations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawyer%20said.%20He%20also%20asked%20the%20public%20to%20refrain%20from%20jumping%20to%20conclusions%20%26quot%3Bbefore%20the%20facts%20come%20out%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FUS%2Fman-arrested-pointing-gun-6-year-boys-head%2Fstory%3Fid%3D104532068%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EABC%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20investigation%20into%20the%20incident%20is%20currently%20ongoing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthe-irony-is-that-elon-musk-after-tesla-wins-autopilot-trial-involving-fatal-crash-4535790%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Irony%20Is%20That...%26quot%3B%3A%20Elon%20Musk%20After%20Tesla%20Wins%20Autopilot%20Trial%20Involving%20Fatal%20Crash%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20this%20comes%20amid%20a%20time%20when%20US%20is%20reeling%20under%20the%20uncontrolled%20and%20widespread%20use%20of%20guns%20across%20the%20country%20which%20has%20resulted%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%20thousands%20of%20innocent%20civilians%20over%20the%20years.%20The%20country%20has%20recorded%20over%20500%20mass%20shootings%20this%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Gun%20Violence%20Archive%20(GVA)%2C%20a%20non-governmental%20organization%20that%20defines%20a%20mass%20shooting%20as%20four%20or%20more%20people%20wounded%20or%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20recent%20shooting%20in%20Maine%20left%2018%20dead.%20This%20attack%20was%20the%20deadliest%20mass%20shooting%20in%202023%20so%20far%2C%20according%20to%20the%20GVA's%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698854700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Fiof8givc_arrest-generic_625x300_30_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-man-arrested-for-pointing-gun-at-6-year-old-boys-head-over-halloween-candy-bag-4536390%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2043-year-old%20man%20in%20the%20United%20States%20has%20been%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20pointing%20a%20gun%20at%20a%206-year-old%20boy%20over%20Halloween%20candy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-man-arrested-for-pointing-gun-at-6-year-old-boys-head-over-halloween-candy-bag-4536390%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-man-arrested-for-pointing-gun-at-6-year-old-boys-head-over-halloween-candy-bag-4536390%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-man-arrested-for-pointing-gun-at-6-year-old-boys-head-over-halloween-candy-bag-4536390%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Maratha%20Reservation%3A%20A%20Timeline%20Of%20Long-Drawn%20Political-Legal%20Battle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20fresh%20wave%20over%20the%20Maratha%20quota%20demand%20in%20Maharashtra%20has%20once%20again%20put%20the%20spotlight%20on%20the%20complex%20politics%20of%20the%20reservation.%20Pro-Maratha%20quota%20protesters%20vandalised%20the%20house%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fncp-mla-prakash-solankes-house-in-maharashtra-set-on-fire-by-protesters-over-maratha-reservation-4527195%5C%22%3EMaharashtra%20lawmaker%20Prakash%20Solanke's%20home%20in%20Beed%20district%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20set%20it%20on%20fire%20Monday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20angry%20mob%20also%20targeted%20an%20office%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%2C%20prompting%20the%20authorities%20to%20tighten%20the%20security%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsecurity-increased-outside-houses-of-ministers-amid-maratha-quota-protests-4532254%5C%22%3EBeed%20and%20parts%20of%20the%20Marathwada%20region%3C%2Fa%3E%20amid%20the%20renewed%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaratha-reservation-without-touching-existing-quotas-eknath-shinde-4534809%5C%22%3Ewho%20chaired%20an%20all-party%20meeting%20today%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20discuss%20the%20fresh%20wave%20of%20statewide%20protests%2C%20said%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20is%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Maratha%20quota.%20Mr%20Shinde%20said%20that%20reservation%20should%20be%20given%20to%20the%20Maratha%20community%20without%20tampering%20with%20the%20existing%20quotas%20of%20other%20communities%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20which%20was%20attended%20by%20NCP%20veteran%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Ashok%20Chavan%20among%20others%20passed%20a%20unanimous%20resolution%20to%20improve%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20Maratha%20reservations%20is%20not%20new%20and%20the%20push%20for%20it%20has%20been%20going%20on%20for%20four%20decades.%20Here%2C%20we%20chart%20the%20Maratha%20quota%20issue%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20Did%20the%20Maratha%20Quota%20Protests%20Start%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EMarathas%2C%20who%20constitute%20nearly%2033%25%20of%20the%20state's%20population%2C%20have%20been%20demanding%20the%20reservation%20in%20education%20and%20government%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%20the%20year%201981%20when%20the%20state%20saw%20its%20first%20protests%20demanding%20the%20Maratha%20reservation%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20Mathadi%20Labour%20Union%20leader%20Annasaheb%20Patil.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20community%20has%20been%20seeking%20Kunbi%20caste%20certificates%20for%20Marathas%20which%20will%20enable%20their%20inclusion%20in%20the%20OBC%20category%20for%20reservation.%20Kunbis%2C%20who%20are%20associated%20with%20agriculture%2C%20are%20grouped%20under%20the%20OBC%20(Other%20Backward%20Classes)%20category%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20when%20the%20Congress%20was%20in%20power%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20government%20brought%20an%20ordinance%20pronouncing%2016%20per%20cent%20reservation%20to%20Marathas.%20The%20Maharashtra%20government%20gave%20its%20nod%20to%20the%20Maratha%20quota%20under%20a%20special%20provision%20in%202018-%20Socially%20and%20Educationally%20Backward%20Class%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHigh%20Court%20Verdict%20In%202019%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202019%2C%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20upheld%20the%20constitutional%20validity%20of%20the%20Maratha%20quota.%20The%20court%20red