making%20him%20a%20very%20useful%20part-time%20spin%20bowling%20option.%20With%20a%20total%20of%20664%20international%20appearances%2C%20he%20is%20the%20most-capped%20player%20of%20all%20time.%20He%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20Team%20which%20won%20the%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20in%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESachin%20has%20played%20six%20IPL%20seasons%20from%202008-2013%2C%20all%20for%20Mumbai%20Indians%2C%20where%20he%20has%20scored%20a%20total%20of%202334%20runs%20in%2078%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2034.84.%20Sachin%20has%2013%20fifties%20and%20one%20hundred%20under%20his%20belt%2C%20hitting%2029%20sixes%20and%20295%20fours%20with%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20119.82.%20He%20won%20the%202013%20edition%20of%20the%20tournament%20with%20the%20franchise%20as%20a%20player.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESachin's%20best%20performance%20came%20in%20IPL%202010.%20He%20scored%20618%20runs%20in%2015%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2047.53%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20132.61.%20He%20scored%20five%20fifties%20that%20season%20and%20his%20best%20individual%20score%20was%2089*.%20He%20won%20the%20'Orange%20Cap'%20that%20season.%20MI%20finished%20as%20runners-up%20that%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20ANI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698847380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fhjl8ti4g_sachin-wc_625x300_01_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fsachin-tendulkars-statue-unveiled-at-wankhede-stadium-where-india-won-the-2011-cricket-world-cup-watch-4535912%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sachin%20Tendulkar's%20life-sized%20statue%20has%20unveiled%20at%20the%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20India's%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20clash%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A134%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fsachin-tendulkars-statue-unveiled-at-wankhede-stadium-where-india-won-the-2011-cricket-world-cup-watch-4535912%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fsachin-tendulkars-statue-unveiled-at-wankhede-stadium-where-india-won-the-2011-cricket-world-cup-watch-4535912%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fsachin-tendulkars-statue-unveiled-at-wankhede-stadium-where-india-won-the-2011-cricket-world-cup-watch-4535912%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMaratha%20Reservation%20Without%20Touching%20Existing%20Quotas%26quot%3B%3A%20Eknath%20Shinde%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20the%20all-party%20meeting%20held%20earlier%20in%20the%20day%20decided%20that%20reservation%20should%20be%20given%20to%20the%20Maratha%20community%20without%20tampering%20with%20the%20existing%20quotas%20of%20other%20communities%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20n%20Mumbai%2C%20Mr%20Shinde%20also%20appealed%20activist%20Manoj%20Jarange%2C%20who%20is%20on%20hunger%20strike%20for%20Maratha%20reservation%20since%20October%2025%2C%20to%20call%20off%20his%20fast%20and%20give%20the%20government%20some%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20decided%20unanimously%20at%20the%20all-party%20meeting%20that%20the%20state%20should%20make%20efforts%20for%20securing%20Maratha%20reservation%20without%20touching%20the%20existing%20quotas%20of%20other%20communities.%20I%20appeal%20and%20request%20Manoj%20Jarange%20to%20withdraw%20his%20fast%20and%20cooperate%20with%20the%20government.%20The%20state%20needs%20some%20time%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20curative%20petition%20filed%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Shinde%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20is%20working%20on%20two%20fronts%20--%20issuing%20Kunbi%20caste%20certificates%20to%20Marathas%20from%20Marathwada%20(so%20that%20they%20can%20avail%20of%20OBC%20reservation)%20and%20preparing%20an%20error-free%20submission%20as%20part%20of%20the%20curative%20petition%20filed%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20all-party%20meeting%20also%20expressed%20its%20disappointment%20over%20the%20violent%20incidents%20reported%20in%20the%20last%20few%20days.%20Such%20violent%20acts%20would%20be%20a%20blot%20on%20the%20Maratha%20community's%20agitation%20for%20reservation.%20The%20state%20government%20needs%20some%20time%20to%20prepare%20a%20submission%20that%20will%20pass%20the%20legal%20test%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20state%20government%20is%20making%20honest%20efforts%20so%20that%20the%20Maratha%20community%20gets%20reservation%20benefits.%20The%20backward%20class%20commission%20is%20working%20on%20a%20war%20footing.%20The%20reservation%20given%20by%20the%20government%20when%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20was%20chief%20minister%20was%20upheld%20by%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20but%20struck%20down%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20some%20errors.%20We%20want%20to%20avoid%20a%20repetition%20of%20this%20situation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shinde%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMaking%20an%20appeal%20to%20Jarange%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20said%20he%20should%20trust%20the%20government's%20efforts.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20of%20some%20violent%20incidents%2C%20the%20common%20man%20should%20not%20have%20any%20safety%20concerns.%20The%20entire%20Maratha%20community%20should%20support%20the%20state%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698847260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fvsec1ssc_eknath-shinde-devendra-fadnavis-ani_625x300_01_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-