2F1719634344614986051%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%201%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EMicah%20Lee%20was%20killed%20in%202019%20after%20their%20Model%203%20veered%20off%20a%20highway%2C%20hit%20a%20tree%2C%20and%20caught%20fire.%20While%20Mr%20Lee%20was%20killed%20in%20the%20incident%2C%20his%20two%20passengers%20were%20injured.%20The%20two%20passengers%20then%20approached%20the%20court%20alleging%20that%20Autopilot%20caused%20the%20accident%20and%20demanded%20over%20%24400%20million%20in%20punitive%20damages.%20This%20trial%20was%20the%20first%20in%20the%20United%20States%20that%20alleged%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftesla-wins-autopilot-trial-involving-fatal-crash-4533143%5C%22%3ETesla's%20autopilot%20feature%3C%2Fa%3E%20led%20to%20death.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETesla%2C%20however%2C%20denied%20liability%20alleging%20that%20Mr%20Lee%20had%20consumed%20alcohol%20and%20that%20it%20was%20unclear%20if%20Autopilot%20was%20engaged%20during%20the%20crash.%20The%20Jury%20in%20Riverside%20County%20Superior%20Court%20also%20voted%20in%20favour%20of%20Mr%20Musk's%20company%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20vehicle%20did%20not%20have%20a%20manufacturing%20defect.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fola-ev-sales-up-by-30-ceo-says-staff-working-more-than-70-hours-to-meet-demand-4535512%5C%22%3EOla%20EV%20Sales%20Up%20By%2030%25%2C%20CEO%20Says%20Staff%20''Working%20More%20Than%2070%20Hours''%20To%20Meet%20Demand%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20major%20victory%20for%20Tesla%20as%20it%20faces%20several%20other%20similar%20lawsuits%20across%20the%20country.%20But%20the%20automaker%20continues%20to%20test%20and%20roll%20out%20its%20Autopilot%20and%20more%20advanced%20Full%20Self-Driving%20(FSD)%20system%2C%20which%20Mr%20Musk%20has%20touted%20as%20crucial%20to%20his%20company's%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%2