s%20in%20Class%2010%20back%20in%202013%2C%20her%20brother%20took%20her%20to%20the%20playground%20and%20introduced%20her%20to%20kabaddi.%20She%20resisted%20participating%20at%20first%2C%20but%20he%20encouraged%20her%20to%20play.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20long%20before%20she%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20game%2C%20she%20recalls%2C%20and%20the%20trajectory%20of%20her%20life%20changed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20simply%20accepting%20that%20she%20would%20get%20married%20when%20she%20reached%20a%20certain%20age%2C%20she%20became%20determined%20to%20make%20her%20own%20decisions.%20Last%20year%20in%202022%2C%20a%20few%20years%20after%20she%20got%20her%20undergraduate%20degree%2C%20she%20interviewed%20with%20Magic%20Bus%20India%20Foundation%20and%20was%20hired%20as%20a%20kabaddi%20coach%20in%20Chandrapur%2C%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20%5Btraditional%5D%20thinking%20is%20that%20boys%20should%20work%20because%20they%20have%20a%20family%20to%20feed%2C%20while%20girls%20are%20expected%20to%20get%20a%20good-looking%20husband%20with%20a%20government%20job.%20But%20my%20brother%20changed%20this%20outlook%20and%20supported%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vidya%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHer%20job%20with%20Magic%20Bus%20inspired%20her%20to%20venture%20even%20further%20outside%20her%20comfort%20zone.%20She%20acquired%20the%20skills%20to%20effectively%20communicate%20with%20school%20principals%20about%20the%20value%20she%20gained%20from%20the%20sports-for-development%20and%20life%20skills%20education%20programmes%20of%20Magic%20Bus%2C%20and%20to%20persuade%20parents%20to%20enroll%20their%20daughters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPermission%20from%20parents%20is%20very%20difficult%20at%20times%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20feel%20%5Bit%20is%5D%20unsafe.%20It%20was%20very%20difficult%20for%20me%20to%20win%20their%20trust%2C%20but%20I%20did%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVidya%20was%20one%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322281%2Fbengaluru-duo-uses-sports-to-help-rural-girls-study-in-school-sportz-village%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esix%20female%20kabaddi%20coaches%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20similar%20backgrounds%20and%20ages%20(between%2023%20and%2025)%20who%20joined%20Magic%20Bus%20around%20the%20same%20time.%20The%20other%20coaches%20were%20Komal%20Pachare%2C%20Nilam%20Verma%2C%20Shital%20Borkar%2C%20Poornima%20Chandekar%20and%20Reema%20Khushwah%2C%20who%20shared%20a%20common%20goal%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F145074%2Flibrary-books-ruchi-dhona-children-education%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20empower%20girls%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20sports%2C%20just%20as%20they%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20them%20are%20part%20of%20Magic%20Bus%E2%80%99%20School%20Completion%20and%20Livelihood%20Enablement%20Programme%20in%20Chandrapur.%20The%20purpose%20of%20the%20programme%20is%20to%20train%20teachers%20to%20deliver%20life%20skills%20education%20to%20adolescents%20from%20Class%206%20to%20Class%2010%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20government.%20Operating%20in%20Chandrapur%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20success%2C%20leading%20to%20Magic%20Bus%20initiating%20a%20partnership%20with%20the%20government%20to%20further%20expand%20their%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMagic%20Bus%2C%20founded%20by%20Matthew%20Spacie%20back%20in%201999%2C%20has%20impacted%20the%20lives%20of%20more%20than%20one%20million%20adolescents%20over%20the%20past%20two-plus%20decades.%20At%20present%203%2C94%2C206%20adolescents%20are%20enrolled%20in%20their%20programmes%20across%202%2C770%20schools.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20the%20initial%20days%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAbout%2030%20years%20ago%2C%20when%20I%20arrived%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20ignore%20the%20stark%20contrast%20in%20living%20conditions%20within%20the%20city.%20On%20one%20side%2C%20there%20was%20a%20sizable%20middle-class%20population%2C%20living%20fairly%20ordinary%20lives.%20On%20the%20other%20side%2C%20there%20was%20a%20parallel%20reality%20of%20people%20living%20in%20poor%20conditions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20outsider%2C%20this%20divide%20deeply%20affected%20me%2C%20compelling%20me%20to%20respond%20in%20some%20way.%20However%2C%20there%20was%20a%20personal%20connection%20that%20played%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20shaping%20my%20vision%20for%20Magic%20Bus.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F8_11zon-1698734921.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22School%20girls%20playing%20football%20in%20their%20campus.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F8_11zon-1698734921.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F8_11zon-1698734921-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F8_11zon-1698734921-500x500.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F8_11zon-1698734921-150x150.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F8_11zon-1698734921-768x768.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F8_11zon-1698734921-96x96.jpeg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333294%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESchool%20girls%20playing%20football%20on%20their%20campus.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESports%20for%20development%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EMagic%20Bus%20India%20Foundation%20is%20a%20pioneer%20in%20the%20life%20skills%20education%20and%20skilling%20sector%20in%20India.%20Their%20mission%2C%20as%20Matthew%20states%2C%20has%20always%20been%20to%20help%20young%20people.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20started%20Magic%20Bus%2C%20our%20aim%20was%20to%20help%20young%20people%20thrive%20and%20find%20happiness%20and%20success.%20We%20took%20them%20on%20mountain%20trips%20and%20engaged%20in%20various%20activities%20to%20boost%20their%20resilience%20and%20happiness.%20Our%20community-based%20mentors%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%2C%20serving%20as%20role%20models%20who%20had%20conquered%20similar%20challenges.%20For%20me%2C%20the%20importance%20of%20mentors%20became%20evident%20early%20on.%20Within%20five%20years%2C%20our%20approach%20transformed%20from%20me%20playing%20rugby%20with%20young%20men%20at%20the%20Gymkhana%20to%20engaging%2010%2C000%20adolescents%20and%20young%20people%20across%20Mumbai%20in%20a%20life-changing%20programme%20led%20by%20mentors%20from%20their%20own%20communities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F317722%2Fmumbai-entrepreneurs-start-marketplace-for-ngo-products-jhappi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20organisation%20%3C%2Fa%3Eimplements%20a%20sports%20and%20activity-based%20life-skills%20programme%20with%20the%20goal%20to%20equip%20adolescents%20with%20essential%20life%20skills%20and%20facilitate%20a%20smoother%20transition%20from%20school%20to%20the%20workforce.%20It%20operates%20in%2024%20states%20across%2072%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F274165%2Ftop-inspiring-indian-villages-sustainable-development%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edistricts%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMagic%20Bus%20has%20played%20a%20pioneering%20role%20in%20introducing%20sports-for-development%20and%20life%20skills%20education%20in%20India%20and%20Southeast%20Asia.%20%E2%80%9CCurrently%2C%20we%20empower%20individuals%20to%20acquire%20essential%20life%20skills%20through%20sports.%20By%20gathering%20on%20the%20playground%2C%20we%20especially%20empower%20girls%20to%20assert%20their%20presence%20in%20a%20domain%20traditionally%20reserved%20for%20boys.%20We%20aim%20to%20challenge%20gender%20stereotypes%2C%20encouraging%20girls%20to%20break%20barriers%20while%20fostering%20equal%20participation%20from%20boys%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jayant%20Rastogi%2C%20Global%20CEO%2C%20Magic%20Bus%20India%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20organisation%20shows%20that%20adolescents%20in%20its%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.magicbus.org%2Fuploads%2Fpdf%2FMB_Impact%2520Report%252022-23.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20programmes%20improved%20their%20school%20regularity%20by%2021.8%25%2C%20a%2031%25%20increase%20in%20perceived%20self-efficacy%2C%20and%20a%2034.7%25%20boost%20in%20resilience.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F5_11zon-1698734990.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22School%20boys%20being%20given%20a%20proper%20coaching%20for%20Cricket.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F5_11zon-1698734990.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F5_11zon-1698734990-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F5_11zon-1698734990-500x500.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F5_11zon-1698734990-150x150.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F5_11zon-1698734990-768x768.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F5_11zon-1698734990-96x96.jpeg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333297%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESchool%20boys%20are%20being%20given%20proper%20coaching%20for%20Cricket.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Baddi%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20a%20place%20where%20Magic%20Bus%20has%20actively%20engaged%20since%202015%2C%20a%20significant%20milestone%20was%20reached%20in%20March%202021.%20The%20organisation%20introduced%20a%20sports%20programme%20exclusively%20tailored%20for%20girls.%20Divided%20into%20two%20distinct%20phases%20from%20December%202021%20to%20March%202023%2C%20this%20programme%20carries%20a%20primary%20objective%20of%20empowering%20girls%20aged%2011%20to%2018%20through%20the%20influence%20of%20sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Vivek%20Sharma%2C%20the%20programme%20manager%2C%2010%2C000%20girls%20were%20given%20sports%20sessions%20each%20in%20kabaddi%20or%20cricket.%20The%20girls%20also%20took%20part%20in%20tournaments%20within%20their%20schools.%20Some%20of%20them%20were%20then%20chosen%20to%20compete%20in%20district%2C%20state%2C%20and%20national%20tournaments.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20objectives%20of%20the%20programme%20also%20include%20the%20holistic%20development%20of%20the%20participants%2C%20which%20includes%20communication%2C%20socio-emotional%20learning%2C%20and%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVivek%20says%20they%20were%20able%20to%20succeed%20in%20Baddi%20because%20Magic%20Bus%20had%20earned%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20trust%20first.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20been%20planning%20since%202015.%20We%20worked%20with%20the%20girls%2C%20the%20boys%20and%20their%20parents%20and%20sensitised%20them%20%5Bto%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20girls%E2%80%99%20sports%20programme%5D.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20programme%20has%20also%20actively%20addressed%20common%20concerns%20raised%20by%20parents%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F162218%2Fuber-cab-women-safety%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eregarding%20the%20safety%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20expenses%20of%20the%20girls%20participating%20in%20tournaments%20held%20in%20larger%20cities.%20Recognising%20these%20concerns%2C%20the%20programme%20takes%20responsibility%20for%20the%20girls%E2%80%99%20expenses%20and%20ensures%20their%20safety%20by%20arranging%20for%20accompanying%20coaches%20during%20their%20travel.%20In%20certain%20cases%2C%20the%20programme%20even%20covers%20medical%20expenses%20and%20provides%20first%20aid%20kits.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVivek%20emphasises%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20way%2C%20we%20address%20any%20doubts%20community%20members%20may%20have%20about%20the%20program%2C%20ensuring%20that%20their%20questions%20are%20answered%20satisfactorily.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMatthew%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20when%20I%20played%20rugby%20with%20young%20people%2C%20I%20believed%20that%20helping%20them%20secure%20jobs%20would%20lead%20to%20economic%20stability.%20However%2C%20we%20realised%20they%20weren%E2%80%99t%20ready%20for%20a%20structured%20work%20environment.%20This%20setback%20inspired%20our%20%E2%80%9CChildhood%20to%20Livelihood%E2%80%9D%20programme.%20We%20understood%20that%20getting%20them%20jobs%20was%20only%20half%20the%20battle%3B%20keeping%20them%20employed%20required%20equipping%20them%20with%20the%20right%20skills%20and%20guidance%20to%20enter%20the%20workforce.%20It%E2%80%99s%20where%20they%20grasp%20the%20value%20of%20work%2C%20learn%20skills%20beyond%20their%20chosen%20profession%2C%20and%20evolve%20into%20role%20models%2C%20actively%20breaking%20the%20cycle%20of%20poverty%20for%20their%20families%20and%20the%20entire%20community.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F3_11zon-1698735055.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20big%20part%20of%20Magic%20Bus%20India%20Foundatio