nability%20and%20resourcefulness%20in%20every%20aspect%20of%20the%20construction%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20reused%20two%20truckloads%20of%20old%20wood%20in%20the%20construction.%20The%20old%20wood%20gives%20a%20typical%20old%20%3Cem%3Ehaveli%3C%2Fem%3E-type%20ambience%20to%20our%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20harvest%20sunlight%20and%20rain%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20ago%2C%20Ramachandrudu%20installed%20an%20off-grid%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F269780%2Fmy-zero-waste-home-saves-70-energy-by-using-the-sun-to-run-appliances%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar%20power%20system%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewith%20a%20capacity%20of%20one%20kilowatt%20to%20fulfil%20the%20household%E2%80%99s%20essential%20energy%20requirements.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20family%20has%20successfully%20reduced%20their%20monthly%20electricity%20bill%20from%20Rs%20800%20to%20a%20mere%20Rs%2080.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20he%20annually%20collects%2040%2C000%20litres%20of%20rainwater%20and%20redirects%20an%20excess%20of%20three%20lakh%20litres%20to%20recharge%20the%20borewell.%20After%20filtering%20water%20through%20sand%20filters%2C%20the%20family%20ensures%20the%20water%E2%80%99s%20purity%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20use%20it%20for%20drinking%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-3-1698759604.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bharani%20has%20also%20made%20unique%20bricks%20from%20styrofoam%20by%20mixed%20it%20with%20cement.%20Close%20to%2070%20percent%20of%20the%20brick%20is%20made%20from%20scrap.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-3-1698759604.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-3-1698759604-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-3-1698759604-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-3-1698759604-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-3-1698759604-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333372%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBharani%20has%20also%20made%20unique%20bricks%20from%20styrofoam%20by%20mixing%20it%20with%20cement.%20Close%20to%2070%20percent%20of%20the%20brick%20is%20made%20from%20scrap.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20make%20our%20own%20chemical-free%20home%20products%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20rainwater%20harvesting%2C%20Ramachandrudu%20has%20implemented%20a%20greywater%20treatment%20system%2C%20which%20effectively%20repurposes%20treated%20greywater%20from%20kitchen%20sinks%2C%20basins%2C%20and%20bathrooms%20for%20watering%20the%20plants%20in%20their%20garden.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20we%20encountered%20a%20foul%20smell%20coming%20from%20nearby%20tanks%2C%20mostly%20from%20the%20accumulated%20dirty%20water.%20We%20realised%20that%20the%20smell%20was%20mostly%20because%20of%20the%20various%20oils%20and%20chemical%20detergents%20we%20used%2C%20which%20polluted%20the%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20adding%20that%20this%20set%20them%20to%20start%20another%20exciting%20experiment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20chemical%20cleaners%2C%20Ramachandrudu%20started%20making%20natural%20cleaners%20using%20a%20blend%20of%20bio%20enzymes%2C%20cow%20dung%2C%20and%20wood%20ash.%20To%20create%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332396%2Fhow-to-make-bio-enzymes-from-kitchen-waste-at-home-diy-steps-by-kolkata-gardener-nita-singh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebio%20enzymes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20collects%20flowers%20and%20lime%20waste%2C%20adding%20natural%20ingredients%20such%20as%20fenugreek%2C%20coconut%2C%20rice%2C%20aloe%20vera%2C%20black%20seeds%2C%20and%20hibiscus.%20These%20elements%20are%20combined%20to%20make%20powerful%20shampoos%2C%20body%20washes%20and%20liquid%20cleaners%20for%20washing%20clothes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20completely%20stopped%20purchasing%20detergents%20from%20the%20market%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThroughout%20these%20years%2C%20the%20father-son%20duo%20embarked%20on%20their%20transformative%20journey%20without%20a%20clear%20plan.%20Rather%2C%20each%20experiment%20served%20as%20a%20catalyst%20for%20the%20next%2C%20leading%20to%20several%20compelling%20and%20innovative%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERamachandrudu%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20glad%20my%20home%20gave%20me%20an%20opportunity%20to%20implement%20my%20ideas%20and%20transition%20from%20advising%20others%20to%20actually%20doing%20something.%20Although%20physically%20exhausting%2C%20it%20has%20brought%20a%20lot%20of%20satisfaction%20my%20way%2C%20both%20at%20the%20professional%20and%20personal%20levels.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Bharani%20and%20Nemani)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESource%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mdpi.com%2F2071-1050%2F14%2F21%2F14393%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESustainability%20Considerations%20of%20Green%20Buildings%3A%20A%20Detailed%20Overview%20on%20Current%20Advancements%20and%20Future%20Considerations%3A%20%3C%2Fa%3EPub