fession%2C%20hailing%20from%20a%20farming%20family%20in%20Sultangunj%20village%20in%20Bhagalpur%2C%20decided%20to%20take%20the%20plunge%20into%20agriculture.%20With%20a%20deep-rooted%20passion%20for%20farming%20and%20a%20vision%20to%20amplify%20the%20value%20of%20the%20produce%2C%20Manish%20embarked%20on%20a%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20having%20a%20GI%20tag%2C%20most%20farmers%20in%20the%20district%20were%20selling%20Katarni%20paddy%20at%20Rs%2030%20per%20kg.%20The%20challenge%2C%20Manish%20says%2C%20was%20that%20%E2%80%9Cfarmers%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20the%20value%20of%20the%20rice.%20Since%20we%20are%20all%20small%20farmers%2C%20we%20were%20not%20able%20to%20get%20the%20right%20price%20or%20find%20the%20right%20people%20to%20sell%20our%20products%20to.%E2%80%9D%20He%20knew%20collectivisation%20was%20the%20only%20way%20to%20ensure%20that%20farmers%20like%20himself%20are%20able%20to%20get%20the%20right%20value%20for%20their%20produce%2C%20Manish%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EManish%20led%20a%20group%20of%20farmers%20to%20form%20the%20Jardalu%20and%20Katarni%20Agro%20Producer%20Company%20Limited%2C%20a%20Farmer%20Producer%20Organisation%20(FPO)%2C%20in%20April%202023.%20Their%20journey%20was%20made%20possible%20through%20the%20support%20of%20Bayer%2C%20working%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Small%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Agri-Business%20Consortium%20(SFAC)%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20developed%20the%20concept%20of%20FPOs%20in%20the%20early%202000s%20to%20enable%20small%20and%20marginal%20farmers%20to%20improve%20their%20access%20to%20investments%2C%20technology%2C%20and%20markets.%20The%20power%20of%20collectivisation%20not%20only%20improved%20production%20efficiency%20but%20also%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20better%20pricing%20strategies%20and%20marketing%20avenues.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHelping%20farmers%20become%20self-reliant%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fbayer1-min-1698759017-scaled.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bayer%20nurtures%20and%20guides%20FPOs%20in%2021%20states%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fbayer1-min-1698759017-scaled.jpeg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fbayer1-min-1698759017-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fbayer1-min-1698759017-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fbayer1-min-1698759017-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fbayer1-min-1698759017-1536x1152.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fbayer1-min-1698759017-2048x1536.jpeg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fbayer1-min-1698759017-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333349%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBayer%20nurtures%20and%20guides%20FPOs%20in%2021%20states.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBayer%20embarked%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20bolster%20FPOs%20five%20years%20ago.%20The%20formation%20of%20FPOs%20is%20very%20important%20to%20support%20small%20farmers.%20Individually%2C%20they%20have%20a%20low%20scale%20and%20cannot%20market%20or%20transport%20their%20products.%20When%20400%20to%20500%20farmers%20come%20together%2C%20they%20have%20an%20opportunity%20to%20collaborate.%20We%20help%20these%20FPOs%20on%20input%20as%20well%20as%20output%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Rajesh%20Singh%2C%20Lead%20%E2%80%93%20Model%20Farms%20and%20Coll