%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20was%20it%20received%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EVishakha%20Bhale%20Vyas%20is%20one%20of%20the%20475%20sports%20allies%20who%20work%20in%20the%20Bharuch%20district%20of%20Gujarat.%20This%20district%20has%20around%2012%2C500%20girls%20aged%20between%20eight%20and%2014%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EResponsible%20for%20mobilising%20and%20supporting%20the%20field%20teams%20in%20the%20district%2C%20she%20also%20pays%20attention%20to%20the%20tournaments%20announced%20by%20the%20local%20and%20district-level%20sports%20associations%20so%20that%20the%20girls%20there%20can%20participate%20in%20those%20events.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20her%2C%20there%20is%20such%20a%20passion%20for%20sports%20that%20in%20the%20district%20they%20have%20branched%20out%20into%20football%20as%20well%20from%20other%20track%20and%20field%20sports%20and%20now%20have%20about%2020%20teams%20of%20girls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20thought%20that%20in%20this%20Jambusar%20block%2C%20which%20is%20very%20backward%2C%20there%20would%20be%20so%20many%20girls%E2%80%99%20football%20teams%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20fact%2C%20our%20girls%E2%80%99%20teams%20have%20been%20the%20only%20ones%20to%20participate%20in%20all%20the%20inter-district%20tournaments.%20Most%20other%20schools%2C%20even%20the%20private%20ones%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20a%20football%20team%20for%20girls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20success%20of%20the%20football%20teams%20in%20turn%20led%20to%20the%20announcement%20of%20a%20training%20programme%20for%20coaches.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20we%20have%20women%20football%20coaches%20who%20have%20D-Level%20Certification%20in%20Coaching%20from%20the%20All-India%20Football%20Federation%20(AIFF)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vyas%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20also%20benefited%20personally.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20student%2C%20I%20played%20kabaddi%20and%20%3Cem%3Ekho%20kho%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20I%20was%20in%20my%20