ng%20outwards%20from%20a%20building)%20articulate%20heritage%20fervour%20even%20from%20a%20distance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKrutarthsinh%2C%20the%20ever-smiling%20host%2C%20is%20now%20taking%20care%20of%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329447%2Fdevra-homestay-in-udaipur-barren-land-to-heritage-property%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eancestral%20property%3C%2Fa%3E%20historically%20known%20as%20the%20Darbargadh%20in%20Devpur%20village%20which%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F270912%2Fchaturbhuj-temple-in-gwalior-has-worlds-oldest-zero-symbol%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E30%20km%20from%20Bhuj%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20is%20now%20known%20commercially%20as%20the%20Devpur%20Homestay.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20a%20few%20rooms%20still%20inhabited%20by%20the%20Jadeja%20family%2C%20the%20vintage%20rooms%20are%20now%20rewriting%20new%20stories%20with%20guests%20having%20access%20to%20various%20suites%20in%20its%20%3Cem%3EMardana%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EZenana%20%3C%2Fem%3E(separate%20male%20and%20female%20quarters%20as%20used%20to%20be%20the%20norm%20back%20in%20the%20day)%20quarters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20property%20also%20houses%20a%20CBSE%20school%20on%20the%20grounds%20for%20students%20up%20to%20class%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20832px)%20100vw%2C%20832px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FP_20171001_092314_HDR_11zon-1698325871.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22832%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22One%20of%20the%20study%20areas%20in%20the%20Gulabi%20Mehdi.%20Picture%20courtesy%3A%20Krutarthsinh%20Jadeja.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FP_20171001_092314_HDR_11zon-1698325871.jpg%20832w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetteri